track_notes: Loop trail to Cat Gap, then the Art Loeb Trail to Chestnut Knob.  Good summit to combine with W4C/CM-081 Cedar Rock Mtn, which is less than 2 miles back along the Art Loeb Trail.
8.1 mile hike with 2560 EG and EL using the full Cat Gap Loop trail and heading both north and south for a double-header of W4C/CM-094 - Chestnut Knob and W4C/CM-081 - Cedar Rock Mtn.
track_title: Cat Gap Loop with Cedar Rock Mtn and Chestnut Knob

track_notes: I followed the Cat Gap Trail clockwise to begin my hike following it to the Art Loeb Trail at Cat Gap.  Turning left on Art Loeb trail to the summit.  On return to CatGap, I continued the Cat Gap Trail as it circles around John Rock to return to the parking area. The return route is less steep but perhaps .5 miles longer.  I will use this route going a coming in the future as it is more gentle.  Dean ~ K2JB
